{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"37fd6ad1ea815cf3d0bda770e1c2a3c134b79edc70ca89e441980064eb60aecf","slug":"blog","location":"/blog.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Blog","content_includes_title":false,"authors":[{"nameParsed":{"literal":"Max Grover","given":"Max","family":"Grover"},"name":"Max Grover","orcid":"0000-0002-0370-8974","url":"https://blog.mgrover.dev","github":"mgrover1","id":"contributors-myst-generated-uid-0"}],"github":"https://github.com/mgrover1/blog","source_url":"https://github.com/mgrover1/blog/blob/main/blog.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/mgrover1/blog/edit/main/blog.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"blog.md","url":"/blog/build/blog-5d1358343320e56dfd88b055913a0075.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can see a full list by year to the left.","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"Lo9ocsO65q"}],"key":"ssOicj5PCR"},{"type":"card","url":"/posts/2025/scipy-2025-takeaways","children":[{"type":"cardTitle","children":[{"type":"text","value":"SciPy 2025 üêç","key":"DdGRthtKSX"}],"key":"JznunGhwat"},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n\n\n:::{caution}\nThis blog post expresses my own personal opinion, not that of my employer.\n:::\n\n:::{figure}\n:label: scipy-selfie\n:align: left\n\n(main_image)=\n![Me in front of the SciPy sign](../images/scipy-selfie.jpeg)\n:::\n\n\nThe term SciPy refers to multiple things - mainly:\n- [SciPy the Project](https://scipy.org/)\n- [SciPy the Community](https://scientific-python.org/)\n- [SciPy the Conference](https://www.scipy2025.scipy.org/)\n\nThis week brought together all three; with the general event being SciPy the","key":"eBXvKSbqUn"}],"key":"I4qqTEfKyw"},{"type":"footer","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Date: ","key":"yEP6oozLT